  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>This course offers you a fast-track to a career in the finance sector. You will develop the knowledge and skills needed to manage your own finances, to become responsible borrowers and sensible savers, and have an appreciation of the need for personal financial planning.</p>
<p>You will also be introduced to all aspects of financial products and services, studying how customers and service providers make decisions.</p>]]></mainContent>
